# 禁止生成文档规则说明

## 规则名称：禁止生成文档

MATCH **/*
EXCEPT **/*.md
EXCEPT **/*.txt
EXCEPT docs/**
EXCEPT README.md

## 禁止生成或修改任何 Markdown 文档

DO NOT create or modify:

- *.md files
- *.markdown files  
- Documentation files
- CHANGELOG, TODO, NOTES
- Inline comments longer than 3 lines
- JSDoc/TSDoc/Python docstrings unless explicitly requested

## 允许的行为

ALLOW:

- Pure code changes
- Refactoring
- Bug fixes
- Feature implementation
- Short inline comments (≤2 lines)

## 明确指令

NEVER write documentation unless I type "please document" or "add docs"
